data.description: Back on the market. Are you looking for elbow room, privacy, no HOA and the perfect home for the fisherman in the family? This home sits on over an acre and features mature trees for privacy. There is a boat dock across the street for use of the neighborhood residents that leads to The Chain of Lakes.  The home is high and dry and not in a flood zone. Inside features include a remodeled kitchen that includes all new appliances, 2 new electrical panels with new GFI breakers in kitchen and bathroom, new windows that open inward for easy cleaning and carpets were updated in 2021. The entire house was painted, inside and out, in 2022.  A/C and septic recently serviced and the washer and dryer stay with the home. The bonus room could easily be closed in for a 3rd bedroom. Outside features include a sprinkler system, new drain fields and new gutters. There is parking for an RV or boat, with a pit for maintenance with electricity and water hook up. Homes in this neighborhood are highly sought after, and are pre permitted for an in-law suite. You will be close to The Villages that offers Medical offices, unique restaurants and shopping. Don't let this one get away.
